" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db687732184990dc3afd05dee57ca9f47aaf7a8e","tid":1588741,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:39:07.000Z","msg":"【召集】23/9 7點太子始創中心唱國歌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587265\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587265</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ebbb04ada1c7f0d9e074cfbbc4f3a3b2c462c719","tid":1588741,"uid":75994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:44:02.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可 黑警死全家 必有天遣"},{"pid":"1773bd7ef46ee86378c3491f39ac6625a74d1a93","tid":1588741,"uid":16775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:45:34.000Z","msg":"想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c80be25c40561bbeb89a44ca462bc5910f5895c8","tid":1588741,"uid":123440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:46:42.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 你班仆街睇曬先講嘢啦"},{"pid":"8947a5e3b5487422917df1624e963cdb71e4837b","tid":1588741,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c80be25c40561bbeb89a44ca462bc5910f5895c8","tid":1588741,"uid":123440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:46:42.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 你班仆街睇曬先講嘢啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:12:33.000Z","msg":"呢幾日咁撚多標題撚，屌極都係咁"},{"pid":"04f6924b4917cc5c7058edb159970f2a1aa7ddd6","tid":1588741,"uid":181502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:16:56.000Z","msg":"假扮標題黨，實際想帶風向，不知所謂"},{"pid":"7f4a9490897b29cc8eb51f19cbcd569ba156f5b3","tid":1588741,"uid":123440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8947a5e3b5487422917df1624e963cdb71e4837b","tid":1588741,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c80be25c40561bbeb89a44ca462bc5910f5895c8","tid":1588741,"uid":123440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:46:42.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 你班仆街睇曬先講嘢啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:12:33.000Z","msg":"呢幾日咁撚多標題撚，屌極都係咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:17:53.000Z","msg":"撚係標題黨 佢講緊係事實 內文都同標題相乎<br />\n<br />\n香港人要真係認清 支持勇武抗爭嘅人係有好大光環 但話就話齊上齊落 去到判刑嗰刻就算幾多人黎聲援都係只得你自己 我地做到嘅只係盡力幫佢地減低壓力<br />\n<br />\n或者好似篇文講 再簡單啲嘅方法 贏咗就得"},{"pid":"bc09ad0d9c03981f85a3ff39a842e653801e8022","tid":1588741,"uid":181502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ca8e216043f068013b12b3e821c3986eee03ff0","tid":1588741,"uid":123440,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:27:07.000Z","msg":"個個睇都未睇 收皮啦屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:18:20.000Z","msg":"唔撚睇呀，講撚咗好多次唔撚好做標題黨"},{"pid":"8d21223f9d7923355ddc6ca331a31c1288b11220","tid":1588741,"uid":249639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:25:02.000Z","msg":"仆街標題黨"},{"pid":"067ec95719ce78021eb0e06d475adac5f51cb941","tid":1588741,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:31:43.000Z","msg":"收皮啦標題黨<br />\n就係試咗好多方法都唔得<br />\n所以咪大家一齊討論緊點行落去囉<br />\n你以為勇武不斷升級就可以迫到無良政府屈服咩<br />\n對家已經打緊國際傳媒牌啦<br />\n我地仲唔醒水<br />\n仲喺度圍住自己轉<br />\n要幫到手足一定要有民眾支持<br />\n行到幾丈遠叫其他人點跟呀"},{"pid":"defc663f4d5971cf98cd4b5cbd713ceb1b882b62","tid":1588741,"uid":317376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:35:45.000Z","msg":"你想講咩係重要， 但係標題黨就係唔得"}]}